.TH "udp4_hwcsum" 9 "udp4_hwcsum" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
udp4_hwcsum \- handle outgoing HW checksumming
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" udp4_hwcsum
.BI "(struct sk_buff *skb "  ","
.BI "__be32 src "  ","
.BI "__be32 dst "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "skb" 12
sk_buff containing the filled-in UDP header
(checksum field must be zeroed out)
.IP "src" 12
source IP address
.IP "dst" 12
destination IP address
